{"tid":342260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老婆大左肚之後好肥好煩又成日發脾氣","createTime":"2017-07-31T12:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T16:52:22.000Z","uid":129221,"like":367,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2aeb8f63d1e22ca15a92ccc09aa32013be559f92","tid":342260,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"為左bb健康我放工就買餸煮飯已經好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要雞翼又話有激素 豆腐又有激素 菜又有農藥<br />\n之後我醒目 求其買啲菜同佢講有機菜買左廿幾蚊斤 豬又係本地豬啦 終於無激到佢掉爛我啲玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知今日我ot左陣 街市都無乜餸賣<br />\n唯有買啲兩餸飯頂住先啦 好在佢都體諒我 無再屌我<br />\n<br />\n我諗左好耐 終於決定左佢個飯係煎魚加菜<br />\n返到屋企我即刻幫佢撩晒啲骨 點知佢都係食到條骨<br />\n佢即刻成碗湯倒埋黎 屌我係咪想吉死bb <br />\n我嬲到仆街 我仲未換衫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都有尊嚴架<br />\n我唔出聲濕住身入左房鎖門打左呢個po出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 我以後唔撚中出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就黎頂唔順啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91d8dd016c70d4fc9a6dbcdc325dc0f7252c0f1","tid":342260,"uid":130706,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"離婚"},{"pid":"200a6136bfa363f5ea86a90a14ab8cb272945c90","tid":342260,"uid":81569,"like":50,"dislike":190,"score":-140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"老婆大肚梗係出去滾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837c45292ae2cc62c07c1d9552e021a77cec8030","tid":342260,"uid":71357,"like":100,"dislike":2,"score":98,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"點解唔召喚伯母或樓主老母幫手照顧啊??<br />\n我識親人有bb都唔會係老公放工都仲未照顧大肚老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=